<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">docker images</code></pre></figure>

<p>Now just run the container and inform which function you want to use, along with its parameters, example: <code class="highlighter-rouge">docker run --rm funcoeszz/zz maiusculas is working</code></p>

